<i>Posted by Canibal on 01-24-2003 09:10 PM:</i>

<p><b> A question of karma</b></p>

<p>Some questions about karma, <br />
<br />
1. is there a post or faq someone could direct me to on the details of obtaining karma? <br />
<br />
2. does the karma spent go away when you cash it in for a particular option? <br />
<br />
3. are there any other forums regularly or irregularly moderated for karma besides general discussion?<br />
<br />
thx</p>

<!-- END TEMPLATE: printthreadbit --><!-- BEGIN TEMPLATE: printthreadbit -->
<hr>
<i>Posted by Bloodshard on 01-24-2003 09:38 PM:</i>

<p><b> Use</b></p>

<p>pray option at the top, it will show you options<br />
<br />
& yes, it goes away when you use it.<br />
<br />
You can possibly get karma for any forum for the can. Usually it's given for inducing productive conversation on the board but may be given out for other reasons.<!-- BEGIN TEMPLATE: postbit_signature -->
