<i>Posted by Odicya on 01-24-2003 11:03 PM:</i>

<p><b> </b></p>

<p>I am pretty much the only person that gives out any Karma. Other mods and admins do it but not nearly as much as I do. I gave out tons of karma when it first was introduced to the board. It was pretty much decided that it was given out more quickly than anticipated. It caused a ton of threads no one ever posted in even though the thread starter posted an intresting topic. <br />
<br />
Karma can not be given in the Rants section or in The Can. Karma is uauly given out when a member of the board proves to be helpful to those asking questions, stimulates a nonflamatory conversation, post something funny, in the monthly Karma games (usualy stuck at the top of the General section).. ect..<br />
<br />
<br />
To use your Karma you select the pray option found at the top of the board under the berthall.com boarder. <br />
<br />
Other forums are watched for karma daily.<!-- BEGIN TEMPLATE: postbit_signature -->
